He's got plenty of good years left in him.

13:32.244 --> 13:34.007
- Oh, he's got 20.
- Sure, you do.

13:34.079 --> 13:35.979
You believe that?
Yeah.

13:36.048 --> 13:38.881
Then why are you giving up on
me? Dad, I'm not giving up on you.

13:38.951 --> 13:41.442
You're talking about
sending me to a sanitarium.

13:41.520 --> 13:47.186
Well, your hearing's still good.
Yeah, it is. And so is my mind.

13:47.259 --> 13:49.693
I don't care what you think,
I'm not crazy.

13:49.762 --> 13:54.358
