17:14.299 --> 17:17.233
I know that. I know that.
But, Al, my God,

17:17.301 --> 17:20.760
if I can prove
that U.F.O. S exist,

17:20.839 --> 17:25.367
<i>I mean, it's as equally as important
as Project Quantum Leap itself.</i>

17:25.444 --> 17:29.073
